Qt 5.15 introduces many new features and improvements as well as bugfixes
over the 5.14.x series. For more details, refer to the online documentation
included in this distribution. The documentation is also available online:

https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/index.html

The Qt version 5.15 series is binary compatible with the 5.14.x series.
Applications compiled for 5.14 will continue to run with 5.15.

Some of the changes listed in this file include issue tracking numbers
corresponding to tasks in the Qt Bug Tracker:

https://bugreports.qt.io/

Each of these identifiers can be entered in the bug tracker to obtain more
information about a particular change.

****************************************************************************
*                               Qt 5.15.0 Changes                          *
****************************************************************************

- [QTBUG-77673] Fixed auto-capitalization so that it's only done after a
  space that follows a sentence-ending character.
- [QTBUG-56918] Fixed input panel not receiving events during modal
  sessions.
- [QTBUG-77753] Fixegd long press behavior of the symbol mode key.
- [QTBUG-79617] Fixed selectByMouse property not being respected when in
  fullscreen mode.
